Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:07.45,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, has embarked on two paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.80,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,One is to find his mother's enemy. A path that leads to the "past".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:19.24,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The other is to turn the world into a place that his sister, Nunnally, can live in happily. A path that leads to the "future".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.48,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,As Lelouch gazes at both the "past" and the "future",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:25.52,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,is the path that leads to the "present", which only he can choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.78,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,the destruction of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.00,CG ON,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,or the reconstruction of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.21,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, I finally understand... You were...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:14.10,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, Mao has...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do that... to your own father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This secret wasn't just your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.48,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's that elderly gentleman called Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Prime Minister of Japan, Kururugi Genbu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:41.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,used his own death to convince and stop the hardline faction,\Nwhich has adopted a do-or-die resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Because a story is needed, be it in Japan or Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1090)}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.81,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.66,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He was different from how he used to be. {Chigai ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.40,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be like this, placing others ahead of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.82,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,So there was a reason behind it. {Literally conspiracy}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.26,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,710)}Suzaku killed his father... and that was when he was just ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.41,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Has he been bearing that all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.60,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lelouch, don't move your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.42,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong. Look down a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.90,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Too low. Look up more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.40,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.45,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Your expression is completely different from what you had at first, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.76,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,A bit like this... and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.31,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,This... All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.78,CG ON,All,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.78,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.35,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,The emotional look was better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.56,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.01,Thoughts,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Isn't the hilarious look better...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.26,Thoughts,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.42,Thoughts,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.62,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the first period math?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.42,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It's because this is Arts Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.90,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? His Highness Clovis made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:44.95,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,On the first day of Arts Week, we will be holding the completion ceremony of this place, the Clovis Arts Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:49.75,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We hope that Princess Euphemia can choose the winning pictures from among those in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.73,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,This picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.98,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:04:01.01,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Based on our investigation, the artist has a quarter of Eleven blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:05.48,CG ON,Euphamia,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, you shouldn't have displayed it at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.53,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's because it's essential to put up a façade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.25,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please take a look at the painting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.77,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's something drawn by the son of Duke Nikolai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.23,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Tako ({\fe128}章魚{\fe1}) literally means octopus, but in this case, it refers to the sausages that are cut into octopus-like shapes. This is usually done as an expression of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.23,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Tako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.64,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.61,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.63,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... this is actually...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.23,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.80,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,They were referred here by Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.75,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...! Shiseiken-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.42,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be blunt. We wish to borrow your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.21,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.94,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Toudou has been held captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.34,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,He sacrificed himself in order for us to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.51,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.90,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Order of the Black Knights is the ally of justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing strange about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Use B13 to gather the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Dismantle the KnightMares and transport them via eighteen routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Get Diethard to oversee this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Inform the regular members to meet up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.65,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. The Chinese Federation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been resolved. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:16.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a hindrance to the plan if your role changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, today is the day that two of the chess pieces I've eyed for a long time gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.08,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the execution date of Toudou Kyoushirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:33.08,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any resistance since the Japanese Liberation Front no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:33.79,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.68,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.06,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Have that man carry out the execution by shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.06,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.60,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you come here so urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.16,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,How's the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.02,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony only starts in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.57,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, the NAC says that there's unrest at Ishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.09,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I guess either the EU or the Chinese Federation is backing them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.42,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,There's confirmed information coming from Ganruu as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.62,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Hokuriku ({\fe128}北陸{\fe1}) refers to the region west of Tokyo. Ishikawa is one of the prefectures within the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.62,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is a great opportunity to stabilize the Hokuriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.00,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave Darlton here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.69,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Ask him for help with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.90,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.34,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We've said it before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.23,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,choose your knight from this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:14.35,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are excellent. Their families are excellent too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.73,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. During winter, the pond will freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.31,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get scolded by Brother if I skate there though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That happened at the Kururugi Shinto Shrine as well, but it was just a small pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.53,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Zarigani ({\fe128}ザリガニ{\fe1}) is a type of crayfish native to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.53,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,There were usually Zarigani... crayfish and other things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.11,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fish for crayfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy. You just need to tie frog legs to the end of the string.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:38.47,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Frogs? The frogs that go, "Croak croak"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.30,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.65,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Though in Japan, we say they go, "Kero kero kero".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.42,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,"Kero kero"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.86,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, "kero kero".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.78,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If things proceed as planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:50.12,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,there will eventually be a day when I won't be around Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.03,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Another case like Mao might happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:55.64,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent that, I need someone to protect Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:00.53,Thoughts,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if Nunnally can become the raison d'être to that someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.04,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.86,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.69,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd-san said there's something urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.47,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:11.82,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.37,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.45,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Can I borrow Suzaku-kun for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.18,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.90,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it'll be fine. That man won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.38,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.42,CG ON,Nunally,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, Suzaku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.36,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.58,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.09,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.70,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk to you about when you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's something important... and serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.16,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? That sounds scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.58,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll meet you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:41.31,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-san is needed by others. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, what do you think about Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.48,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.44,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I like Brother the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.45,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, I'll head off first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.21,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me you meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.38,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.17,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.97,CG ON,Reporter00,0000,0000,0000,,In regards to the construction of this museum, it's said that Eleven companies were excluded from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.96,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... About that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.40,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,It's still being investigated. Please pardon our inability to reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.11,CG ON,Reporter01,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. It's pointless to ask Princess Euphemia about politics, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:33.86,CG ON,Reporter02,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kellyman from Interstate. There are rumors lately that say you are selecting your knight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:38.67,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Yes... Knight... Erm... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.78,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:44.55,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Please restrict your questions to those about the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.61,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to mix up the hydraulics?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.61,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,But this is different from the Burai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:03.95,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Is working together with the Order of the Black Knights the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.76,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way to save Colonel Toudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.02,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto has promised that they'll lend us new machines as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.76,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,However, principles and claims are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.91,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,We are not nationalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:15.82,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.87,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about these petty things after the Colonel's been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:22.77,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. My place is wherever Toudou-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.72,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already. Just put the damn thing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.53,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time before the operation starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.54,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Be more gentle with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:29.92,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:29.92,CG ON,Other,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.30,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,It's made of something a hundred times more delicate than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.10,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.47,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The mother of that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.08,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So you are Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.81,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I've heard various rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Rakshata, same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen various news articles on the internet about you in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.50,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Articles about the usage of cybernetics for medical purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.94,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,I hate talking about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.82,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.86,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Presents from Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.64,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.13,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Will the synchronization rate really increase with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.53,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,It won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.04,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.92,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The survival rate will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.02,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The executioner has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.38,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.43,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's someone you know. Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.86,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.12,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.24,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's Her Highness Cornelia's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.54,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,the formalities need to be observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:49.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This change of executioner is a case that's exceptional among the exceptional after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.34,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.83,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.31,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're freed from this document hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.29,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, we are on our way to save you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.17,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,This Gekka sure is amazing. A big difference from the Burai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.67,CG ON,Kosetsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.34,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.58,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The synchronization with the attached weapons is still imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.44,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that isn't a problem with the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.21,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,There's a 0.07 deviation with the cognizance process.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:54.01,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because those old guys at Kyoto didn't give us better parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:58.59,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from the top: I'm to execute you before you get taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.30,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:04.10,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,This life has already been forsaken. I don't have any lingering attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall take over that life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:06.99,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.00,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.52,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou Kyoushirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:30.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The only man who scored a victory against the Britannians during the war seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.52,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,The Miracle of Itsukushima? Are you seeking my miracle as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was a victory achieved through information-gathering and tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.98,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.10,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:46.16,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,The master I serve, General Katase, is no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.03,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,I am now just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.03,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You must take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility for the miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:03.92,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The resistance movement in Area 11 is obviously more intense than those in the other Areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is because Japan was forced into submission while she still had power remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:11.23,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They want to see the continuation of the dream called the "Miracle of Itsukushima".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.85,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.76,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People tend to indulge in the illusions called "miracles".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:20.44,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why Refrain is spreading so rampantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle, Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle on desperately till the very end, then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:29.51,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Until the name "Toudou the Miracle" gets shredded into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.91,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,After that, will the Japanese, for the first time, accept the truth of our defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.04,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's necessary for the sake of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can make that fleeting dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:47.55,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,With that, Her Highness, Princess Euphemia will now select the grand winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:52.00,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The work that this flower is placed on will be the grand winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.50,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.13,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Toudou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.63,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, sorry to have caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.05,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.55,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Assist Zero.{intentionaly bled}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.37,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the remaining troops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.24,CG ON,Shiseiken,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,With this, all the conditions have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.15,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have chosen Nunnally's knight as well. All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.29,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why... is that thing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:41.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. The remaining problem has come charging in on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:46.59,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, isn't it time for you to make your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.33,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.04,Thoughts,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:52.68,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.09,CG ON,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.37,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,The captive is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.94,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.81,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. The enemy's new machines sure are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.20,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,But Cecile-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.30,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.36,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,If you view it solely by result,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:20.19,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it lucky that the only transportation device left here is the trailer with the Lancelot onboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:24.33,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the result is solely dependent on the Lancelot, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:28.07,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the white armor that Zero is having problems with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.13,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.55,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.29,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is reckless. It's seven against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.97,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,But that KnightMare called "Lancelot" is pretty powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.33,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow, he evaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.59,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.22,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, white knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.60,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Send out everything to provide cover for Kururugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.52,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Report that the terrorist has been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.37,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, do you have any information about that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.34,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you can follow my orders from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.80,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All units, widen the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.61,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That speed and maneuverability is indeed a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:08.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There is a certain pattern that fellow moves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A frontal attack will come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He won't make a pinpoint attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:18.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once his attack is evaded, he will quickly move to launch his next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Analyze his movement data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,X57!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.67,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... He really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:34.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. In such a situation, his next action... will be to jump back to widen the distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.86,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The coordinate is X23!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:36.93,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:41.70,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.14,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,He evaded my triple thrust?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:44.75,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.17,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah! This is bad. It doesn't have an escape block yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.76,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't installed it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.64,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Suzaku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.62,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:09.90,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, the orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.81,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your next orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:12.55,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything so far was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.28,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.67,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Eleven! If I remember correctly, that's Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.91,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The one from His Excellency, Clovis's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.58,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Why is an Eleven inside a KnightMare?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.37,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.90,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the video transmission! If this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.97,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:32.34,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.75,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.22,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.97,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Suzaku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.84,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah. Toudou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still wish to continue living even after breaking your own principles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.88,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.52,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you execute me as planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You should be beside Nunnally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.36,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.07,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come here to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.83,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Have you degenerated into a useless brat who's satisfied with the present?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.03,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless to go against the current society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:13.09,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A power that accepts it and tries to change it is then truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.85,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.87,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.90,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should travel down that path!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.42,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:24.27,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Be it victory or defeat, you won't achieve anything unless you do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:26.81,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,The same applies whether it's at the national or personal level!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.62,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.67,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, are we going to capture him or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.36,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.61,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Destroy the white armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.19,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for Zero's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.46,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.89,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Senba, Freely Rotational Life-or-Death Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.06,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:45.24,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! If you do it right now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.91,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's an attack from four directions. There's no way to evade it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.96,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Suzaku, release the Haken Booster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.15,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,The password is my favorite thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.38,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:02.93,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,What the..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.59,CG ON,Kosetsu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:11.85,CG ON,Shougo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:14.02,CG ON,Ryouga,0000,0000,0000,,An interesting way of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.31,CG ON,Nagisa,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina, turn to the left! This time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.40,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.57,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.06,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Continuing this fight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.91,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We have achieved our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Use route three...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We will retreat immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.13,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,A battle you can't win and a battle lost are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.50,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, looks like you know that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:41.67,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.68,CG ON,Toudou,0000,0000,0000,,Release the chaff smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.33,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.23,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Have they repelled the Order of the Black Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.36,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.48,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he chase after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.92,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're fellow Elevens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.92,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I was wondering how he was able to take them on even though it was seven against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.95,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.12,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.51,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I will answer the question raised earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.55,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You were wondering whether I had decided on who would be my knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.59,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The one I have decided on to be my knight is the person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.30,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.83,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Toudou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:40.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.61,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,am your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:51.02,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is not coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:53.19,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He didn't reply even when I called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.08,CG ON,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:48.40,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My friend, Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:51.57,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What during that seven years of blank space changed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:56.82,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, since I became Zero, that fellow must just be putting on some kind of false mask as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:24:00.63,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Had our fate been laid out for us ever since that summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:02.12,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.22,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who my enemy is.
